## **Installation**

To install `rosamllib`, you can use `pip`:

```bash
pip install rosamllib
```
Alternatively, you can clone this repository and install it manually:

```bash
git clone https://gitlab.com/ucla_rosaml/shared/rosamllib
cd rosamllib
pip install .
```

